(72, 10, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextMobile is launching an exciting new mobile service that offers truly unlimited usage across Canada, Mexico, and the United States with no roaming fees. Your mission is to create a simple prompt for an AI to generate a product description for this groundbreaking service. Focus on a clear directive.</p>'),
(73, 10, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(74, 10, '_resources', '<p>Use the following resources to help you complete this challenge:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary\">Sample Resource 1 - To be created</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-primary\">Sample Resource 2 - To be created</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>These resources will help you understand the fundamentals of prompt engineering and guide you through creating effective prompts for AI text generation.</p>'),
(75, 10, '__resources', 'field_64dd19ef99238'),
(76, 10, '_links', ''),
(77, 10, '__links', 'field_64dd1a2199239'),
(78, 10, '_solution', '<p>Great job! By using only a simple prompt, you have generated a product description. As we continue, you will uncover the countless possibilities that AI has to offer when you learn to refine and enhance your prompts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Key takeaways from Day 1:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>A prompt is your way of communicating with an AI model</li>\r\n<li>Clear directives lead to better outputs</li>\r\n<li>Simple prompts can produce effective results</li>\r\n<li>Focus on being specific about what you want the AI to generate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Get prepared for Day 2!</strong> Tomorrow we\'ll explore how to enhance and refine your prompts for even better results.</p>'),
(79, 10, '__solution', 'field_64dd1a2d9923a'),
(80, 12, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">At NextData, your recent trade show event was a great success. Many prospects visited your booth and expressed interest in seeing a product demo. Your team now wants to send a follow-up email to these prospects. Your task is to segment the event list, identify the prospects who indicated interest in the demo, and schedule a follow-up email.</p>'),
(81, 12, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(82, 12, '_resources', '<p>On Day 1, you imported the event attendee list, but the team forgot to include the information about the prospects who requested to see the demo. A new file has been sent, which includes a new \"product_demo_interest\" column. If the value in this column is \"Yes,\" it indicates that the prospect would like to see a demo. Below, you will find the email template and the copy for the follow-up email.</p>\r\n\r\n<!-- Table start -->\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Dataset</h3>\r\n<table class=\"table table-striped\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope=\"col\">email</th>\r\n<th scope=\"col\">product_demo_interest</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>mlawther0@sciencedirect.com</td>\r\n<td>Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>phutcheon1@telegraph.co.uk</td>\r\n<td>No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>cpossell2@github.io</td>\r\n<td>Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>gdirkin3@latimes.com</td>\r\n<td>Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>zdaveren4@eventbrite.com</td>\r\n<td>Yes</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- Table end -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Button start -->\r\n<a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/mc30/blob/main/ae30-03-event-attendees.csv\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">ð¾ Download .csv</a>\r\n<!-- Button end -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Template start -->\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/em_event_followup.png\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/em_event_followup.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1 mx-auto\">\r\n		</a>	\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-03-em-event-followup.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-03-em-event-followup\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">ð Email Preview</a></div>	\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Template end -->'),
