(332, 162, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">As a marketer, your goal is to improve the impact of every communication, including emails. Today, your challenge is to invite trade show attendees to the product launch event, but with a twist: you will test two different subject lines using the email A/B testing feature in list emails. This test will help determine the subject line that results in the highest open rates.</p>'),
(333, 162, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(334, 162, '_detail', '<p>Today, you will explore the world of email marketing and learn about the capabilities of Account Engagement that can help you make better decisions. Your task is to conduct A/B testing on two different subject lines for an invitation email for the product launch event.</p>'),
(335, 162, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(336, 162, '_resources', '<p>You can use the email template that you imported on Day 1. Simply update the copy and subject lines for the email. To preview the email and view different subject lines, click on each email below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/day-6-email.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/day-6-email.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-01-em-event-thankyou.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-06-em-event-invite-A\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">ð Email Preview A</a></div>	\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-06-em-event-invite-B\" class=\"btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">ð Email Preview B</a></div>\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>'),
