(650, 378, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">Senior executives play crucial roles in decision-making. NextData will be hosting a special after-event reception exclusively for these executives. Your task is to send personalized invitations to these individuals. Please ensure that the email includes a correct greeting, taking into account that some records may be missing the first name or last name.</p>'),
