(652, 378, '_detail', 'Day 9 brought an interesting challenge where you are required to send an exclusive, personalized invite to senior level (C-level and VP) executives for an after-event reception. You need leverage Handlebars Merge Language (HML) to display a default value if prospectâs first name is missing.'),
