(687, 386, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData has an event registration page and wants to create a dynamic confirmation page that displays a different message to senior executives compared to other registrants for the product launch event. As a marketer, your task is to implement this personalization using MCAE\'s built-in features.</p>'),
(688, 386, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(689, 386, '_detail', 'For Day 10 of the MCAE30 Challenge, you are tasked with creating a dynamic confirmation page to deliver a personalized message to senior executives. You will be creating a dynamic content with Job Title as a criteria to show a different message when a senior executive fills our the form.'),
(690, 386, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(691, 386, '_resources', '<p>For this challenge, you will be leveraging the form that you created on Day 2. Haven\'t had a chance to create a landing page yet? You can use the layout template below to create the landing page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-event-promotion.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-event-promotion.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/AE30-02-LT-Event-Promotion.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-02-lp-nextdata-event-promotion\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>\r\n'),
