(893, 435, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData provides two main solutions: Data Analytics and Data Management. Your marketing team is interested in gaining a deeper understanding of how prospects are interacting with each solution. Your mission today is to set up page actions to monitor these interactions and categorize the prospects based on their engagement levels for each solution.</p>'),
(894, 435, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(895, 435, '_detail', 'Today, your task is to categorize and track prospects\' interests in Data Analytics and Data Management solutions. By setting up Page Actions and using Scoring Categories, you can monitor and adjust the engagement experience for each solution.'),
(896, 435, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(897, 435, '_resources', '<p>To assign different scoring categories to each page, you need to create a new landing page. One option is to close the demo request layout template and create an alternative landing page. You can refer to the layout template for guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-13-lp-thumbnail.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-13-lp-thumbnail.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-13-lt-demo-request.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae-14-lp-nextdata-demo-request\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>'),
