(1017, 460, '_resources', '<p>To complete today\'s challenge, you will need at least two landing pages to use in Multivariate Testing. You can utilize the same research paper layout template to create a new landing page.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<!-- col-1 start -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-19-lp-a.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-19-lp-a-thumb.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-19-lt-nextdata-resource-a.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-19-lp-nextdata-resource-a\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview A</a></div>		\r\n	</div>\r\n	<!-- col-1 end -->\r\n	<!-- col-2 start -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-19-lp-b.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-19-lp-b-thumb.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-19-lt-nextdata-resource-b.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-19-lp-nextdata-resource-b\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview B</a></div>		\r\n	</div>\r\n	<!-- col-2 end -->	\r\n</div>'),
