(1095, 486, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">The marketing team at NextData is interested in gathering more information about leads and contacts who engage with the recent research paper. They have asked if it is possible to automatically add prospects who download the research paper to a Salesforce campaign with a specific status. Your task for today is to automate this process within Account Engagement.</p>'),
(1096, 486, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1097, 486, '_detail', 'For Day 21, you turn your attention towards Salesforce Campaigns. You are tasked to add any prospect who downloads an asset to the respective Salesforce campaign automatically, and set their status to \"Responded\".'),
(1098, 486, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1099, 486, '_resources', '<p>You have taken a break from creating new assets for the past three challenges, and now is a great time to focus on platform capabilities. If you haven\'t already created the research paper landing page, you can use the layout template provided below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-16-landing-page-2.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-16-landing-page-2.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-16-lt-nextdata-resource.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-17-lp-nextdata-resource\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div>                   \r\n</div>'),
