(1173, 506, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">One of the main goals of NextData\'s marketing team is to maintain a healthy prospect database. The team aims to remove anyone from the database who has not engaged with any content in the past six months. As the marketer at NextData, your task is to come up with a solution to achieve this goal.</p>'),
(1174, 506, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1175, 506, '_detail', 'On Day 23, we will focus on the silent observers in your prospect list - those who haven\'t engaged with any content. Your task is to find a solution that identifies these prospects. You can make use of dynamic lists and list views to accomplish this challenge.'),
(1176, 506, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1177, 506, '_resources', '<p>There is no need to create any email or landing page elements for this challenge. If you haven\'t imported the initial prospect list from the Day 2 challenge to Account Engagement, you can find it below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Dataset</h3>\r\n<!-- Table start -->\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n  <table class=\"table table-striped\">\r\n    <thead>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">first_name</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">last_name</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">email</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">job_title</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">city</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">country</th>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </thead>\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>Mabelle</td>\r\n        <td>Lawther</td>\r\n        <td>mlawther0@sciencedirect.com</td>\r\n        <td>Analytics Team Manager</td>\r\n        <td>Milwaukee</td>\r\n        <td>United States</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>Paulie</td>\r\n        <td>Hutcheon</td>\r\n        <td>phutcheon1@telegraph.co.uk</td>\r\n        <td>Senior Business Analyst</td>\r\n        <td>Markham</td>\r\n        <td>Canada</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>Cherey</td>\r\n        <td>Possell</td>\r\n        <td>cpossell2@github.io</td>\r\n        <td>Econometrician</td>\r\n        <td>Wabana</td>\r\n        <td>Canada</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>Gretal</td>\r\n        <td>Dirkin</td>\r\n        <td>gdirkin3@latimes.com</td>\r\n        <td>Streaming Data Specialist</td>\r\n        <td>Dieppe</td>\r\n        <td>Canada</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>Zedekiah</td>\r\n        <td>Daveren</td>\r\n        <td>zdaveren4@eventbrite.com</td>\r\n        <td>Real-time Data Analyst</td>\r\n        <td>Walnut Grove</td>\r\n        <td>Canada</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Table end -->\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/mc30/blob/main/ae30-01-event-attendees.csv\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">ð¾ Download .csv</a>'),
