(1244, 518, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">Data consent is a critical aspect of NextData\'s operations, ensuring compliance with data regulations and respecting the privacy of their prospects. As an experienced marketer, you have been tasked with creating a process that sends emails to prospects whose consent date is 180 days old, asking them to confirm their consent to continue receiving communications from NextData.</p>'),
(1245, 518, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1246, 518, '_detail', 'Today\'s challenge is to automate a process that sends an email to prospects whose consent date is 180 days old. To accomplish this, you will utilize the Engagement Studio program in a new manner to meet operational requirements. Additionally, you need to create a landing page where potential customers can confirm their consent. When the form is submitted, the consent date should be updated. You will also need to create email templates for use in the Engagement Studio program. This task is essential for compliance with the law and ensuring respectful communication with potential customers.'),
