(1290, 526, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">At NextData, the first experience for new customers is crucial. Your task is to create a welcome email that offers them the option to choose their onboarding experience. This not only facilitates the early adoption of NextData services but also provides valuable insights for future communications.</p>'),
(1291, 526, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1292, 526, '_detail', 'Today, your task is to create a welcome email for NextData\'s new customers. This email should direct them to a custom preference center, where they can select their onboarding preferences. By doing so, we can determine which emails they should receive during the onboarding process. This challenge will help you learn how to create visually appealing forms and effectively utilize data from these customer journeys in your campaigns.'),
(1293, 526, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1294, 526, '_resources', '<p>To practice today\'s task, you can import a new dataset that includes the customer account launch date. You will use this data point to trigger an onboarding email. Additionally, if you would like to match the landing page with the same look as below, you will need to import a new landing page layout.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Dataset</h3>\r\n<!-- Table start -->\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n  <table class=\"table table-striped\">\r\n    <thead>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">email</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">account_launch_date</th>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </thead>\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>mlawther0@sciencedirect.com</td>\r\n        <td>18/02/2024</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>phutcheon1@telegraph.co.uk</td>\r\n        <td>30/07/2024</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>cpossell2@github.io</td>\r\n        <td>19/01/2024</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>gdirkin3@latimes.com</td>\r\n        <td>06/01/2024</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>zdaveren4@eventbrite.com</td>\r\n        <td>09/02/2024</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Table end -->\r\n\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/mc30/blob/main/mcae30-27-onboarding.csv\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">ð¾ Download .csv</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<!-- Templates -->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<!-- Templates: 1st Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-27-em.png\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-27-em.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1 mx-auto\">\r\n		</a>	\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-27-em-welcome.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-27-email-preview\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">ð Email Preview</a></div>				\r\n	</div> \r\n	\r\n	<!-- Templates: 2nd Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-27-lp.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-27-lp-thumb.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-27-lt-custom-preference.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-27-lp-customer-preferences\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div> 	\r\n</div>'),
