(1319, 534, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData is interested in understanding how their prospects engage with their emails. As a marketer, your task is to incorporate a sentiment widget into the email templates. This interactive feature will allow prospects to click on an image and provide instant feedback.</p>'),
(1320, 534, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(1321, 534, '_detail', 'Day 28 improves your knowledge of email marketing by introducing an interactive feature: an email feedback widget. This feature utilizes form handlers in a unique way to collect instant feedback from prospects. Your task is to create a widget that includes three links. Whenever a subscriber clicks one of these links, the response will be saved in MCAE.'),
(1322, 534, '__detail', 'field_64e26bc8efb7b'),
(1323, 534, '_resources', '<p>To direct subscribers to a specific page after they click on a link in the email, you will need a landing page. You can use the thank you page template below for the landing page. As for the email itself, you can choose one of the previous email templates. If you\'re in need of a new template, you can download one below.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<!-- Templates -->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<!-- Templates: 1st Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-28-em.png\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-28-em.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1 mx-auto\">\r\n		</a>	\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-email-templates/blob/main/ae30-28-em-welcome.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Email Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/ae30-28-email-preview\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\"  target=\"_blank\">ð Email Preview</a></div>				\r\n	</div> \r\n	\r\n	<!-- Templates: 2nd Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-5\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-28-lp.png\">\r\n		<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-28-lp.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1\">\r\n		</a>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/account-engagement-layout-templates/blob/main/ae30-28-lt-email-feedback.html\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">â¬ï¸ Layout Template</a></div>\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://www.nextinc.xyz/email-feedback\" class=\"btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill\" target=\"_blank\">ð Landing Page Preview</a></div>		\r\n	</div> 	\r\n</div>