(1365, 545, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextData aims to send renewal reminder emails to customers before their contract expires, ensuring they are aware of the expiration and can make informed decisions about renewing. Your challenge is to automate this process, using these emails to gently remind customers and showcase any new features or upgrades available.</p>'),
