(1367, 545, '_detail', 'On the last day of MCAE30, your goal is to improve NextData\'s customer engagement efforts. To achieve this, you will be responsible for implementing a process that effectively engages customers and ensures their continued loyalty. Your key task is to create an engagement studio program that sends a renewal reminder email 30, 15, and 1 day prior to a customer\'s contract expiration. '),
