(1369, 545, '_resources', '<p>In most organizations, information about contract renewals is usually obtained from your CRM. For this challenge, you can import the sample data into Account Engagement. Before importing, make sure to create a new field called <strong>Contract Renewal Date</strong> to map it to the corresponding field in the sample dataset. The email copy is also provided below for your reference.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Dataset</h3>\r\n<!-- Table start -->\r\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n  <table class=\"table table-striped\">\r\n    <thead>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">email</th>\r\n        <th scope=\"col\">contract_renewal_date</th>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </thead>\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>mlawther0@sciencedirect.com</td>\r\n        <td>2023-12-26</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>phutcheon1@telegraph.co.uk</td>\r\n        <td>2024-01-18</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>cpossell2@github.io</td>\r\n        <td>2024-01-09</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>gdirkin3@latimes.com</td>\r\n        <td>2023-12-21</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td>zdaveren4@eventbrite.com</td>\r\n        <td>2024-01-17</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Table end -->\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://github.com/sabuhiy/mc30/blob/main/mcae30-30-contract-renewal.csv\" class=\"btn btn-success rounded-pill text-white\" target=\"_blank\">ð¾ Download .csv</a>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"fs-5 my-4 text-success\">Templates</h3>\r\n<!-- Templates -->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<!-- Templates: 1st Column -->\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n		<a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-34-em-30.png\">\r\n			<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/day-34-em-30.png\" class=\"img-fluid border rounded-1 p-1 mx-auto\">\r\n		</a>	\r\n		<div class=\"d-grid mt-3\"><a href=\"https://github.