(1616, 434, '_criteria', 'In earning the Explorer badge, participants have mastered the fundamentals of Account Engagement over the first seven days. This journey involved importing prospect lists, creating engaging emails and landing pages, and initiating their first steps in A/B testing. Through these tasks, participants have not only grasped the essentials of email marketing within Account Engagement but also laid a solid foundation for more complex marketing strategies, setting the stage for further exploration and skill development in the world of digital marketing.'),
(1617, 434, '__criteria', 'field_65b5d53936fe6'),
(1618, 479, '_criteria', 'The recipient has earned the Pathfinder badge, a significant milestone in their Account Engagement journey from Days 15 to 21. During this period, they delved into advanced topics in Marketing Cloud Account Engagement, including list segmentation, enhancing user interaction through page actions, and conducting email marketing strategy tests using A/B testing. They also utilized engagement studio programs and incorporated feedback mechanisms into their email campaigns. This badge signifies their proficiency in leveraging the functionalities of Marketing Cloud Account Engagement to strategically plan and implement digital marketing strategies.'),
