(2270, 718, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">The Marketing team has noticed an increase in unsubscribes from their email campaigns. They are evaluating multiple scenarios to identify the root cause. In one scenario, they want to check if the number of unsubscribes changes throughout the week. Your task is to examine the unsubscribe data and determine the number of unsubscribes per day of the week.</p>'),
