(2363, 789, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextMobile\'s marketing team is launching a new high-speed fiber internet service and needs to quickly generate promotional content for various marketing channels. The content team is overwhelmed with requests from different departments and needs a faster way to create initial drafts of marketing messages. Your challenge is to write a simple, effective prompt that can generate compelling marketing copy for NextMobile\'s fiber internet service.</p>'),
