(37, 2, '2023-08-17 16:43:15', '2023-08-17 16:43:15', '<strong>Step 1: Prepare Your List</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Create a CSV file containing your prospect data with headers such as email, first name, last name, company name, job title, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Navigate to Imports</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Account Engagement Settings</strong> > <strong>Imports</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Import a file</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click on the <strong>+Upload File</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-2a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-2a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Choose Your File</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Upload your CSV file and check the compliance box.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-3-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-3-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Map Fields</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Map the columns in your CSV file to the corresponding fields in Account Engagement.</li>\r\n  <li>If necessary, check the \"overwrite existing data\" box to update information for existing prospects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Select Campaign and Tags</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Choose a campaign that aligns with the source of the prospects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-5-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-5-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 6: Select Action</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Select <strong>Import prospects and add to list(s)</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-6-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-6-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 7: Confirm and Save</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click <strong>Confirm and Save</strong> to initiate the import process. You will receive a notification once the prospects have been imported.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-7-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/import-list-7-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to import a list', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-import-prospects-and-create-lists-in-pardot', '', '', '2023-11-13 23:41:31', '2023-11-13 23:41:31', '', 0, 'https://mc30.zoompcreative.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=37', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
