(66, 1, '2023-09-11 08:24:17', '2023-09-11 08:24:17', '<strong>Step 1: Prepare Your List</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>Create a CSV file containing your prospect data with identifiable fields such as company name, job title, email, first name, and so on.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Log into Pardot</strong>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Make sure you have Admin rights for this task.</li>\n	<li>Navigate to Admin > Import > Prospects.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/import-list-2-edited.png\" alt=\"import list to pardot\" class=\"img-fluid\"/>\n\n<strong>Step 3: Choose Your File</strong>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Upload your prepared CSV file and check the compliance box.</li></ul>\n\n<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/import-list-3-edited.png\" alt=\"chose your file\" />\n\n<strong>Step 4: Map Fields</strong>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Link the columns in your CSV file with the appropriate fields in Pardot. Remember that the email address field is mandatory.</li>\n<li>If necessary, select the âoverwrite existing dataâ box to update information for existing prospects.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/import-list-4-edited.png\" alt=\"map fields\" />\n\n<strong>Step 5: Select Campaign and Tags</strong>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Associate your list with a campaign that reflects where the prospects came from.</li>\n<li>Use tags for better organization and additional context about the prospect source.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/import-list-5-edited.png\" alt=\"select campaign and tag\" />\n\n<strong>Step 6: Select Action</strong>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Decide what you want to do with the imported prospects. You can add them to a new list, globally opt out the prospects, or just import them into your Pardot environment.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/import-list-6-edited.png\" alt=\"Select action\" />\n\n<strong>Step 7: Confirm and Save  ð</strong>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Review your actions and save them. Pardot will notify you via email once the prospects are imported.</li>\n</ul>\n\n![import-list-7-edited.png](https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/81743b7e-1acd-48f0-a9ff-f496268f5f9f/import-list-7-edited.png)\n\n**Note**: For better organization, consider using a consistent naming convention for your lists.', 'How to import a list into Account Engagement', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '37-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-09-11 08:24:17', '2023-09-11 08:24:17', '', 37, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?p=66', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
