(93, 1, '2023-09-12 16:08:27', '2023-09-12 16:08:27', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Layout Templates</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to Content > Layout Templates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/layout-template-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/layout-template-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Layout Template</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the \'+Add Layout Template\' button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/layout-template-2.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/layout-template-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Name Your Template</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Please provide a name for your layout template, for example, \"Event Template\". Additionally, add a tag to help you identify and organize your templates internally.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/layout-template-3.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/layout-template-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Define the Layout</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Go to the Layout tab and copy and paste your custom HTML and CSS styling here.</li>\r\n  <li>Make sure your template includes the following variable tags:</li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>The <strong>%%title%%</strong> is displayed in the browser window.</li>\r\n    <li>The <strong>%%description%%</strong> is a meta-description that is only visible to search engines. It provides information about your landing page.</li>\r\n    <li>The <strong>%%content%%</strong> refers to the designated area for the form.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <li>If you have a custom CSS to format your forms, ensure that the checkbox for \"Include default CSS stylesheet (recommended)\" is unchecked.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-layout-3.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-layout-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Save Your Layout Template</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>After completing all updates and previewing your layout template, click on <strong>Save</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'How to create a layout template', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-a-layout-template-in-account-engagement', '', '', '2023-11-14 00:09:40', '2023-11-14 00:09:40', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=93', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
(95, 1, '2023-09-13 13:24:26', '2023-09-13 13:24:26', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to the Forms Page</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Content</strong> > <strong>Forms</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-1-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-1-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Form</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the <strong>+Add Form</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Name the Form</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Choose a name for your form and select a folder to save it in.</li>\r\n  <li>Associate the form with a campaign and click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Configure Fields</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>By default, four fields will be present: First Name, Last Name, Company, and Email. You can add additional fields by clicking <strong>+ Add New Field</strong>.</li>\r\n  <li>Click <strong>Next</strong> to proceed and update the look and feel of your form.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-3-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-3-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Customize Look and Feel</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Choose a layout template for your form and update the Submit Button text.</li>\r\n  <li>After configuring the look and feel, click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 6: Set Completion Actions</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Decide what should happen after a prospect submits the form. Configure the \'Thank You Content\' as per your requirement.</li>\r\n  <li>Review and confirm the form\'s layout, fields, and completion actions. Once all details are confirmed, click <strong>Next</strong> and then <strong>Confirm & Save</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-5-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-5-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to create a form', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-a-form-in-account-engagement', '', '', '2023-11-13 23:53:22', '2023-11-13 23:53:22', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=95', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
