(120, 1, '2023-09-16 18:11:05', '2023-09-16 18:11:05', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Segmentation Lists</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to Prospects > Segmentation Lists.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-1a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-1a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Dynamic List</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click the <strong>+ Add List</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Add the List Information</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Assign a name to your list.</li>\r\n  <li>Select a folder to store the dynamic list.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Enable Dynamic List</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Enable the <strong>Dynamic List</strong> option to enable automatic updates of your list based on the set criteria.</li>\r\n  <li>Click on <strong>Set Rules</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-3-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-3-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Set Dynamic Rule Criteria</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Select the match type:</li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><strong>Match All</strong>: Prospects need to meet all the listed criteria.</li>\r\n    <li><strong>Match Any</strong>: Prospects can meet any one of the rules.</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <li>Add individual criteria by clicking + Add new rule. For more complex criteria sets, you can use + Add new rule group.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 6: Preview and Confirm</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>You have the option to preview the list before generating the full list.</li>\r\n  <li>If you are satisfied with the list preview, click <strong>Run Rules</strong>. The list will then populate with prospects that meet your criteria, and it will continue to update as new prospects meet the conditions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-5-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-5-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to create a dynamic list', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-a-dynamic-list-in-account-engagement', '', '', '2023-11-14 01:01:08', '2023-11-14 01:01:08', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=120', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
(121, 1, '2023-09-17 05:35:52', '2023-09-17 05:35:52', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Form</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to Content > Forms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-1.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2: Select the form to edit</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click on the form you would like to add a completion action and click on the <strong>Edit Form</strong> button.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-2a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-2a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 3: Add a Completion Action</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Navigate to the <strong>Completion Actions</strong> tab. Scroll down to the <strong>Completion Actions</strong> section and choose the desired action type from the dropdown menu. The available actions include \"Add tags,\" \"Add to campaign,\" \"Add to list,\" and more.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 4: Define Action Details</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Once you have chosen the desired action type, you will need to specify the parameters for that action. For example, if you choose <strong>Add tags</strong>, you will need to select which tag you want to add to the prospect.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-4a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-4a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 5: Save Your Changes</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Click <strong>Next â«</strong> to proceed and <strong>Confirm & Save</strong> to publish your changes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-5a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/completion-action-5a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\r\n', 'How to add a completion action to forms', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-add-a-completion-action', '', '', '2023-11-14 01:08:45', '2023-11-14 01:08:45', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=guide&#038;p=121', 0, 'guide', '', 0),
