(192, 1, '2023-11-13 23:50:52', '2023-11-13 23:50:52', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to the Forms Page</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to <strong>Content</strong> > <strong>Forms</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-1-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-1-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Form</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the <strong>+Add Form</strong> button.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 3: Name the Form</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Choose a name for your form and select a folder to save it in.</li>\n  <li>Associate the form with a campaign and click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-2a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 4: Configure Fields</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>By default, four fields will be present: First Name, Last Name, Company, and Email. You can add additional fields by clicking <strong>+ Add New Field</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Click <strong>Next</strong> to proceed and update the look and feel of your form.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-3-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-3-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 5: Customize Look and Feel</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Choose a layout template for your form and update the Submit Button text.</li>\n  <li>After configuring the look and feel, click <strong>Next</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-form-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 6: Set Completion Actions</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Decide what should happen after a prospect submits the form. Configure the \'Thank You Content\' as per your requirement.</li>\n  <li>Review and confirm the form\'s layout, fields, and completion actions. Once all details are confirmed, click <strong>Next</strong> and then <strong>Confirm & Save</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/a14d5357-89cb-4670-be5e-ab07bce35243/create-form-5-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/a14d5357-89cb-4670-be5e-ab07bce35243/create-form-5-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n', 'How to create a form', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-11-13 23:50:52', '2023-11-13 23:50:52', '', 95, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?p=192', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
