(210, 1, '2023-11-14 01:00:40', '2023-11-14 01:00:40', '<strong>Step 1: Navigate to Segmentation Lists</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>In your Account Engagement dashboard, go to Prospects > Segmentation Lists.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-1a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-1a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 2: Add New Dynamic List</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the <strong>+ Add List</strong> button.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2a.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2a.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 3: Add the List Information</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assign a name to your list.</li>\n  <li>Select a folder to store the dynamic list.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-2-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 4: Enable Dynamic List</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Enable the <strong>Dynamic List</strong> option to enable automatic updates of your list based on the set criteria.</li>\n  <li>Click on <strong>Set Rules</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-3-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-3-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 5: Set Dynamic Rule Criteria</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>Select the match type:</li>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Match All</strong>: Prospects need to meet all the listed criteria.</li>\n    <li><strong>Match Any</strong>: Prospects can meet any one of the rules.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <li>Add individual criteria by clicking + Add new rule. For more complex criteria sets, you can use + Add new rule group.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-4-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://marketingcloud30.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/create-dl-4-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n\n<strong>Step 6: Preview and Confirm</strong>\n<ul>\n  <li>You have the option to preview the list before generating the full list.</li>\n  <li>If you are satisfied with the list preview, click <strong>Run Rules</strong>. The list will then populate with prospects that meet your criteria, and it will continue to update as new prospects meet the conditions.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"border rounded-3 p-2 mb-3\"><a data-fslightbox href=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/9172b77b-b657-459a-a30c-dbbd8e21d618/create-dl-5-edited.png\"><img src=\"https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/cb78aac7-4a17-40ec-86da-d22b1e00b600/9172b77b-b657-459a-a30c-dbbd8e21d618/create-dl-5-edited.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></a></div>\n', 'How to create a dynamic list', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '120-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-11-14 01:00:40', '2023-11-14 01:00:40', '', 120, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?p=210', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
