(790, 2, '2025-06-28 16:11:13', '2025-06-28 16:11:13', 'Welcome to Day 2 of the NextMobile Prompt Engineering Challenge!\r\n\r\nYesterday, you crafted your first basic prompt. Today, we build on that by introducing Prompt Templates â a way to create reusable frameworks for your prompts, saving you time and ensuring consistency across your marketing materials.', 'Day 2 - Prompting vs. Prompt Engineering', 'Learn to create reusable prompt templates for efficient and consistent content generation across different products and services.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'p8q2v5', '', '', '2025-07-05 09:44:31', '2025-07-05 09:44:31', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=challenge&#038;p=790', 2, 'challenge', '', 0),
(791, 2, '2025-06-28 16:41:33', '2025-06-28 16:41:33', 'Welcome to Day 3 of the NextMobile Prompt Engineering Challenge!\r\n\r\nYou\'ve learned the basics of prompts and how to use templates. Today, we focus on the essential skill of Prompt Engineering â the art and science of refining your prompts through trial and error to get the best possible results from the AI. It\'s about understanding that your first prompt might not be perfect and being willing to iterate.', 'Day 3 - Iterative Refinement', 'Learn the essential skill of prompt engineering through iterative refinement to get the best possible results from AI.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'r3n8k4', '', '', '2025-07-05 18:15:14', '2025-07-05 18:15:14', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=challenge&#038;p=791', 3, 'challenge', '', 0),
(792, 2, '2025-06-28 17:04:16', '2025-06-28 17:04:16', 'Welcome to Day 4 of the NextMobile Prompt Engineering Challenge!\r\n\r\nYou\'ve now experienced basic prompting and the iterative nature of prompt engineering. Today, we solidify your understanding by clearly defining the difference between these two approaches. While prompting is the act of providing input, prompt engineering is the deliberate and often multi-step process of refining that input to achieve a desired outcome.', 'Day 4 - Mastering Strategic Prompting', 'Understand the crucial difference between simple prompting and strategic prompt engineering for complex marketing tasks.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'w5t9m2', '', '', '2025-07-05 19:31:43', '2025-07-05 19:31:43', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=challenge&#038;p=792', 4, 'challenge', '', 0),
(793, 2, '2025-06-28 23:23:00', '2025-06-28 23:23:00', 'Welcome to Day 5 of the NextMobile Prompt Engineering Challenge!\r\n\r\nYou\'re building your prompt engineering skills by understanding fundamentals and using templates. Now, let\'s add another layer of control: Role Prompting. By telling the AI who to be, you can dramatically change the style and voice of its output, making it perfect for creating content tailored to specific audiences or mimicking authentic voices.', 'Day 5 - Master Role Prompting', 'Master role prompting to transform AI communication by assigning specific personas that match different audiences and contexts perfectly.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'b7n4k9', '', '', '2025-07-06 03:35:53', '2025-07-06 03:35:53', '', 0, 'https://marketingcloud30.com/?post_type=challenge&#038;p=793', 5, 'challenge', '', 0);
