(57, 5, 'tabs_0_tab_content', '<!-- row start -->\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n\r\n<!-- col left start -->\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<p>MCAE30 offers a unique way to learn Marketing Cloud Account Engagement (MCAE) through daily challenges. Each daily challenge has been carefully designed to cover every topic you will encounter in MCAE. We strive to make the use-case scenarios in each challenge as close as possible to real life. Participants are expected to spend between one and two hours to complete challenges. By the end of the 30-day challenge, you will learn:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Learn how to navigate the platform to complete various marketing operations tasks.</li>\r\n<li>Create and send various marketing assets, including but not limited to email templates and landing pages.</li>\r\n<li>Gain a solid understanding of lead lifecycle management and how MCAE integrates with Salesforce.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- col left end -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- row end -->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'),
