(2373, 790, '_description', '<p class=\"mb-0\">NextMobile\'s social media manager has been using basic prompts to create content, but the results are inconsistent and often miss the mark for different audience segments. The marketing director wants to see more strategic, targeted content that speaks directly to specific customer needs. Your challenge is to transform a basic prompt into a strategically engineered prompt that produces more targeted, effective marketing content for NextMobile\'s services.</p>'),
(2374, 790, '__description', 'field_64dd19ca99237'),
(2375, 790, '_challenge_detail', '<h3>Task:</h3>\r\n<p>Create a prompt template for generating social media posts about different NextMobile products or services. The template should include placeholders for the product/service name and its key selling points or benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Example Prompt Template:</h5>\r\n<pre><code class=\"txt\">Write a compelling social media post about [PRODUCT/SERVICE NAME]. Highlight the following key benefits: [BENEFIT 1], [BENEFIT 2], and [BENEFIT 3]. Keep the tone engaging and include a call to action to learn more at [LINK].</code></pre>'),
(2376, 790, '__challenge_detail', 'field_challenge_detail_ref'),
(2377, 790, '_resources', '<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/research/constitutional-ai-harmlessness-from-ai-feedback\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-secondary\">Prompt Engineering vs Basic Prompting - Anthropic Research</a></li><li><a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/improve-marketing-messages\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-secondary\">Strategic Marketing Message Development - HubSpot Blog</a></li></ul>'),
(2378, 790, '__resources', 'field_64dd19ef99238'),
(2379, 790, '_solution', '<p><strong>Strategic Prompt Engineering</strong> is the targeted refinement technique - it transforms basic prompts into precise instructions that generate content tailored to specific audiences, tones, and business goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here\'s how <strong>Strategic Prompt Engineering</strong> works:</p>\r\n\r\n<!-- Prompt Layout starts -->\r\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-white my-5 rounded-4 border border-1\">\r\n    <!-- Prompt #1 starts -->\r\n	<div class=\"bg-light ms-5 p-4 rounded-4\">\r\n		Write a compelling 2-sentence marketing message for NextMobile\'s new high-speed internet service targeting busy professionals who work from home. Use an enthusiastic but professional tone and emphasize productivity benefits.\r\n	</div>\r\n	<!-- Prompt #1 ends -->\r\n	<!-- Prompt Output #1 starts -->\r\n	<div class=\"mt-4\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-1\">\r\n				<span class=\"svg-icon svg-icon-sm text-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-bs-placement=\"top\" aria-label=\"abs/abs046.svg\" data-bs-original-title=\"abs/abs046.svg\">\r\n                <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n                  <path d=\"M8 22C7.4 22 7 21.6 7 21V9C7 8.4 7.4 8 8 8C8.6 8 9 8.4 9 9V21C9 21.6 8.6 22 8 22Z\" fill=\"#035A4B\"></path>\r\n                  <path opacity=\"0.3\" d=\"M4 15C3.4 15 3 14.6 3 14V6C3 5.4 3.4 5 4 5C4.6 5 5 5.4 5 6V14C5 14.6 4.6 15 4 15ZM13 19V3C13 2.4 12.6 2 12 2C11.4 2 11 2.4 11 3V19C11 19.6 11.4 20 12 20C12.6 20 13 19.6 13 19ZM17 16V5C17 4.4 16.6 4 16 4C15.4 4 15 4.4 15 5V16C15 16.6 15.4 17 16 17C16.6 17 17 16.6 17 16ZM21 18V10C21 9.4 20.6 9 20 9C19.4 9 19 9.4 19 10V18C19 18.6 19.4 19 20 19C20.6 19 21 18.6 21 18Z\" fill=\"#035A4B\"></path>\r\n                </svg>\r\n              </span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-11\">\r\n				Transform your home office into a productivity powerhouse with NextMobile\'s lightning-fast internet service. Say goodbye to buffering and hello to seamless video calls, instant file uploads, and uninterrupted workflow!\r\n			</div>			\r\n		</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n	<!-- Prompt Output #1 ends -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Prompt Layout ends -->\r\n\r\n<h5>Key Insight</h5>\r\n<p>Prompt engineering involves deliberate refinement and optimization for specific goals. By adding audience specification, tone guidance, and context constraints, you create more targeted, effective results than basic prompting.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Try This Yourself</h5>\r\n<p>Test these variations and see how small changes affect the output:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\">\"Write about NextMobile\'s customer service for frustrated customers experiencing service issues\"</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\">\"Create a 2-sentence social media response about NextMobile\'s customer service with empathetic but reassuring tone\"</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\">\"Generate a marketing message for NextMobile\'s 5G service targeting gamers who need low latency\"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Common Pitfalls â</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Over-engineering simple tasks:</b> Not every prompt needs multiple constraints</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Conflicting instructions:</b> \"formal yet casual\" confuses the AI</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Vague targeting:</b> \"customers\" is too broad, \"busy professionals\" is specific</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Pro Tips â</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Define specific audiences:</b> \"busy professionals\" vs \"customers\" creates different outputs</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Specify tone clearly:</b> \"professional but enthusiastic\" prevents generic corporate speak</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Add purposeful constraints:</b> \"2-sentence\" or \"include specific benefits\" guides output</li>\r\n<li class=\"mb-1\"><b>Test and compare:</b> Always compare basic vs engineered results to see improvement</li>\r\n</ul>'),
