(2500, 799, '_description', 'NextMobile is launching a major campaign for the new UltraConnect Pro smartphone. The team needs several short, attention-grabbing ad variations for digital platforms. You have some examples of successful past ad copy. Your challenge is to test the impact of providing a different number of these examples in your few-shot prompts and analyze how the AI\'s generated ad variations change.'),
(2501, 799, '_detail', '<h5>Task</h5>\n<p>Write two few-shot prompts to generate a short ad variation for the NextMobile UltraConnect Pro.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Use only one example of a short, punchy ad.</li>\n<li>Use five examples of short, punchy ads.</li>\n<li>Compare the generated ad variations from both prompts.</li>\n</ol>');

